song_name: Allergic To Thoughts Of Mother Earth
Allergic To Thoughts Of Mother Earth

version_description: This version of mine aims at a chord version of this fabulous song by Placebo. These lyrics are such poetry, Brian Molko is always true to form. Love it. To me, it appears beautiful (and more comfortable to fingers) to even half step it up (playing, so, A- instead of G#-). Anyway, chords are: E and G#- all along the song and during. Choose the rythm that best fits to your ear (during the chorus it changes, fastening up).
This version is just the base chords from the song, I've added in some dynamics like palm muting to give the song some texture but it's optional.
